# PVARA Email Configuration
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your email credentials

# Email Service Configuration (Using Gmail)
EMAIL_USER=your-email@gmail.com
EMAIL_PASSWORD=your-app-password-here

# Backend API URL (default for local development)
REACT_APP_API_URL=http://localhost:5000

# ===== GMAIL SETUP INSTRUCTIONS =====
# 1. Enable 2-Factor Authentication on your Gmail account
# 2. Go to: https://myaccount.google.com/apppasswords
# 3. Generate an App Password for "Mail"
# 4. Copy the 16-character password (without spaces)
# 5. Paste it in EMAIL_PASSWORD above
# 6. Save this file as .env (remove .example)
#
# For production, consider using:
# - SendGrid (https://sendgrid.com)
# - AWS SES (https://aws.amazon.com/ses/)
# - Mailgun (https://www.mailgun.com)
